tnote.storage

Class MasterFileHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • tnote.storage.MasterFileHandler

  • public class MasterFileHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages the master files necessary in TNote. Paths to each master file are saved in this class. Each master file is a text file stored in a common folder. Information can be saved or extracted from each master file.
    Author:
    A0124131B
